(320, "JESSIE FARRELL: FREE COMMUNITY EVENT", " <p> JESSIE FARRELL<br> Monday, February 13th, 2017 at 2:00pm<br> Family Day<br>  West Vancouver Community Centre<br> Free Admission<p> Featuring the music from her children&#39;s music album, &quot;Take Me Outside&quot;.<br> The catchy and whimsical songs are featured in a kids&#39; CBC television series &quot;Scout & The Gumboot Kids.&quot; Inspired by motherhood and her own children&#39;s imagination, Jessie has expanded from her award-winning country music roots to lively musical storytelling for her young fans!</p></p>", "http://vancouver.eventful.com/events/jessie-farrell-free-community-event-/E0-001-097017643-2?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '10:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
