(323, "Human Rights Professional Development Training for York Staff and Graduate Students", " <br><strong>Location:</strong> A226 Glendon campus <br><br>Oct 26, 2016, 1pm-2pm<p><p>The Human Rights Professional Development Training Program consists of one-hour training sessions.<p><strong>Employment Equity & Race</strong><p>In this workshop, participants will receive an overview of the goals and principles of the Employment Equity program at York University. Participants will gain an understanding of the impact of microaggressions and implicit bias on racial equity in the workplace and obtain tips on reducing and eliminating these barriers. </p></p></p></p>", "http://toronto.eventful.com/events/human-rights-professional-/E0-001-097256701-8@2016111500?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '48:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
