(876, "London Community Orchestra - Young Soloists Concert", " <ul><li></li></ul><br><p><strong>Camille Saint-Saëns</strong><br> Violin Concerto no. 3 in b, Op. 61<br>   -Joshua Lee, violin<br><br><strong>Nikolai Rimsky-Korsakov</strong><br> Piano Concerto in c-sharp, Op. 30<br>   -Matthew Zhou, piano<br><br><strong>Alexander Arutiunian</strong><br> Concerto for Trumpet and Orchestra<br>   -Patrick Smithers, trumpet<br><br> Our featured young soloists concert is always a big hit each year!  The concert will feature three incredibly talented young musicians who will be performing for their first time with an orchestra.  In May, our soloists were chosen by auditioning with their respective concertos, and they showed amazing talent that we can&#39;t wait to share with you!<br><br><em>Sponsoring our young soloists concert is Greta Toni Swart</em><br><br><strong>Single ticket prices:</strong><ul><li>Adults: $18.00<li>Seniors: $15.00<li>Students: $12.00<li>Children: 12 and under: $5.00</li></li></li></li></ul><p><strong>Single tickets are available:</strong><ul><li>Orchestra members<li>At the door<li>Online tickets available: <a href="http://www.onstagedirect.com/lco" rel="nofollow">www.onstagedirect.com/lco</a></li></li></li></ul><br><a href="http://www.londontourism.ca/Events/Music/London-Community-Orchestra--Young-Soloists-Concert#" rel="nofollow"></a></p></p>", "http://eventful.com/events/london-community-orchestra-young-soloists-concert-/E0-001-097032211-0?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '06:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
