(1145, "P.A. Day Camps at Ontario Science Centre", " <p>Escape the ordinary and spend an action-packed day at the Science Centre filled with fun, hands-on discovery. Make new friends, take part in lively science experiments and enjoy exclusive access to the exhibit halls. No parents allowed – kids ages 5-12 only!<p><em><strong>DATES:</strong></em><p><strong>October 7, 2016: Weather Wise  </strong><br> Venture into the new Wild Weather exhibition and explore the meteorological marvels that affect our world.<br><em>Book by October 5, 4 p.m.</em><p><strong>November 18, 2016: Cosmic Quest</strong><br> Explore the night sky and investigate mysteries of our solar system that are out-of-this-world!<br><em>Book by November 16, 4 p.m.</em><p><strong>December 2, 2016: Flight School  </strong><br> Lift off! Build a glider and watch it soar as you experiment with the forces of flight.<br><em>Book by November 30, 4 p.m.</em><p><strong>January 20, 2017: Watts Matter  </strong><br> Spark your curiosity at our new Energy Show and experiment with some super-fun physics of your own.<br><em>Book by January 18, 4 p.m.</em><p><strong>February 17, 2017: (Not So) Simple Machines</strong><br> Explore the new exhibition The Machine Inside: Biomechanics and create a cool contraption inspired by the innovative illustrator, Rube Goldberg.<br><em>Book by February 15, 4 p.m.</em></p></p></p></p></p></p></p>", "http://toronto.eventful.com/events/pa-day-camps-ontario-science-centre-/E0-001-097001492-9?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '24:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
