(1393, "FA16ULP Urban Landscape Painting (B/I/A) with TBD", " Tuesdays 6:30-9:30pm for 9 weeks/27hrs If you look at the urban scape and sense it&#39;s soul, or see a kind of beauty that triggers an emotional response, this class is for you. Urban landscape or urban scape, can be many things, as one can find many different things within a city. Students will work from photographs, preferably their own, of urban scenes. The process will include constructing the composition, deciding on a focal point, and choosing scale, size and technique. Instructor will help you by guiding you through the process, and navigate you to explore your own mind, and to search for meaning of chosen image through the painting process. Techniques may be demonstrated, and examples of relevant work shown. Materials list will be given. ", "http://toronto.eventful.com/events/fa16ulp-urban-landscape-p-/E0-001-095983886-5@2016111018?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '01:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
