(1394, "FA16WP Watercolour Painting (B/I/A) with Marija Barac Jandric", " Thursdays 9:30am-12:30pm for 10 weeks/30hrs This course is for all who wish to improve their watercolour skills and technique. Each student is approached on their own level and instruction adapted to help every student further develop technically as well as conceptually. As the skills strengthen so does students&#39; confidence. Demonstrations are available, and experiments encouraged, while the students dictate the pace. Materials list will be provided. ", "http://toronto.eventful.com/events/fa16wp-watercolour-painti-/E0-001-095983872-2@2016111009?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '06:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
