(1396, "FA16PPK Painting Portraits of Kids (B/I) with Jane Mikas", " Fridays 1:00-4:00pm 9 weeks/27hrs It&#39;s not easy to paint kids portrait well. People mostly just copy from photographs with varying results. In this course we will also work from photos, but we will learn how to &quot;read&quot; the photo, and how to build a natural and believable image of a child capturing the energy and livelyness instead of stiffness.   ", "http://toronto.eventful.com/events/fa16ppk-painting-portrait-/E0-001-095984133-7@2016111013?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '03:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
