(1413, "Helping with Furniture | Nov 30th", " Volunteer opportunity that runs EVERY WEDNESDAY evening - Go once, go when you are available, go every week - its up to you. What will you do: Organizers will send you the meeting place the day before you are to volunteer.  This changes each week based on the donations being picked up. You will attend a variety of locations in Ottawa picking up donated furniture. You will take these donations back to a storage unit in the east end. From there you will fill a truck with donated furniture and deliver it to the homes of families in need (specific locations to be determined on a weekly basis).  It is amazing!! You will need a car or  will need to attend with someone who has a car ( carpool and go as a group)   AND be sure to dress for the weather.  Note: end time depends on how many people volunteer and is just an estimation ", "http://ottawa.eventful.com/events/helping-furniture-nov-30th-/E0-001-096759200-1?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic", "INTERVAL '04:00:00' HOUR TO MINUTE", NULL);
