(1436, "FA16DPPS Drawing/Painting of People, Portraits and Selfies with Nada S. R.", " Thursdays 1:00-4:00PM for 10 weeks/30 hrs You will learn how to create portraits and self portraits using various materials and techniques, with live models and/or from photography.  INSERT INTO evenement
(noEvenement, titre, description, siteWeb, duree, imageAffiche)
